            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We tell people all the time to keep their vehicles out of sigh in a secured facility instead of just parking them in the driveway. While that certainly helps cut down on theft, it’s certainly no guarantee someone who doesn’t want to make a living honestly won’t still help themselves to your stuff. That’s exactly what happened in Bertrand, New Brunswick, Canada recently as some suspects broke into a warehouse, stealing two Camaros and a truck.",
