            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " say the suspect(s) towed away the Chevy pickup using a black Ford F-150, which you can see in screen capture of surveillance footage. Sadly, with how common F-150s are that might not be much to go on. Still, the public is being asked to help if they have any information about these vehicles or the suspect(s).",
